queries.name: imdb_dataset.profiling-name_basics_model_cleansed-nconst-value-frequencies-text
queries.sql:
WITH
    value_frequencies AS (
        SELECT "nconst" AS value_, COUNT(*) AS frequency_
        FROM main_imdb_silver.name_basics_model_cleansed
        WHERE "nconst" IS NOT NULL
        GROUP BY "nconst"
    ),
    frequent_values AS (
        SELECT CAST('frequent_values' AS VARCHAR) AS metric_, ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY frequency_ DESC) AS index_, value_, frequency_
        FROM value_frequencies
        ORDER BY frequency_ desc
        LIMIT 10
    )
SELECT *
FROM frequent_values
ORDER BY metric_ ASC, index_ ASC
